N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 149.3 - Identification of adolescent diversion part-eligible actions or proceedings

State Regulations

Procedures shall be established in each
criminal court in the county where an adolescent diversion part has been
created to identify matters eligible for transfer to such part following
arraignment. Notes
